Marlene Forte https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Marlene_Forte 0 Ana Marlene Forte Machado is a Cuban American actress and producer. She is known for her role as Carmen Ramos on the TNT drama series, Dallas (2012–2014). Ana_Marlene_Forte_Machado is a_Cuban_American_actress_and_producer .
